{"title":"the 2nd 一些控顶手法","date":"2023-08-31T10:38:30.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 31, 2023","L":"08/31/2023","MM-DD":"08-31"},"link":"2023/08/31/the-2nd-一些控顶手法","tags":["sleight of hand"],"updated":"2023-08-31T12:08:41.138Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>控顶手法</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Marlo’s Tilt<br>\ndouble undercut<br>\nfan shuffle</p>\n</blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"首先声明！！！跟赌博无关\">首先声明！！！<s>跟赌博无关</s><a title=\"#首先声明！！！跟赌博无关\" href=\"#首先声明！！！跟赌博无关\"></a></h2>\n<p><font color=\"\" size=4 face=\"\"><strong>第一款是Marlo’s Tilt</strong></font><br>\n<font color=\"blue\" size=4 face=\"楷体\">首先先由观众抽出一张牌，让观众记下，之后插在在整幅牌的中间<s>看似中间</s>之后打开第一张牌，不是观众的选择，但晃荡一下，观众的牌就出现了。</font><br>\n<font color=\"\" size=4 face=\"\"><strong>第二款是double undercut</strong></font><br>\n<font color=\"green\" size=4 face=\"楷体\">首先先由观众抽出一张牌，让观众记下，之后把这张牌插到中间位置，再从下面往上面作两次切牌，牌就控制到顶上了</font><br>\n<font color=\"\" size=4 face=\"\"><strong>第三款是overhand shuffle</strong></font><br>\n<font color=\"red\" size=4 face=\"楷体\">首先先由观众抽出一张牌，让观众记下，之后把这张牌插到中间位置<mark>注意是一边开上面牌的扇一边把牌插入中间</mark>,之后把扇翻过来时整理整幅牌，牌就到了顶部。</font><br>\n<img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/08/31/pPwzUKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/08/31/pPwzsP0.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n电脑用户觉得好，别忘了<kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>D</kbd>加入收藏哦！</p>\n<h3 id=\"explanation:\">EXPLANATION:<a title=\"#explanation:\" href=\"#explanation:\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[^Marlo’s Tilt]:Controlling card to the 2nd place<br>\n[^double undercut]: 在切牌时手指抵住空隔位置，在把下面分两段切上<br>\n[^fan shuffle]:展牌时把那张牌拨到下面，用扇盖住牌时收起底下的牌即可</p>\n</blockquote>\n","next":{"title":"My 1st card Trick","link":"2023/08/27/My-1st-card-Trick"},"plink":"https://space.bilibili.com/588129/2023/08/31/the-2nd-一些控顶手法/","toc":[{"id":"首先声明！！！跟赌博无关","title":"首先声明！！！跟赌博无关","index":"1","children":[{"id":"explanation:","title":"EXPLANATION:","index":"1.1"}]}],"reading_time":"307 words in 2 min"}